}}'''海马旁回'''（英文：Parahippocampal gyrus）是环绕[[海马体|海马体]]的[[大脑皮层|大脑皮层]][[灰质|灰质]]区，属于[[边缘系统|边缘系统]]/[[边缘叶|边缘叶]]的一部分<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|title=Parahippocampal Gyrus - an overview|url=https://www.sciencedirect.com/topics/neuroscience/parahippocampal-gyrus|accessdate=2021-04-05|work=|publisher=ScienceDirect|language=en|archive-date=2021-10-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211021112642/https://www.sciencedirect.com/topics/neuroscience/parahippocampal-gyrus|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":22" />。 海马旁回在[[记忆|记忆]]存储和调取的过程中扮演重要角色（尤其[[空间记忆|空间记忆]]和导航）<ref name=":0" /><ref>{{Cite journal|title=Role of the parahippocampal cortex in memory for the configuration but not the identity of objects: converging evidence from patients with selective thermal lesions and fMRI|url=https://www.frontiersin.org/articles/10.3389/fnhum.2015.00431/full|last=Bohbot|first=Véronique D.|last2=Allen|first2=John J. B.|date=2015|journal=Frontiers in Human Neuroscience|doi=10.3389/fnhum.2015.00431|volume=9|language=en|issn=1662-5161|last3=Dagher|first3=Alain|last4=Dumoulin|first4=Serge O.|last5=Evans|first5=Alan C.|last6=Petrides|first6=Michael|last7=Kalina|first7=Miroslav|last8=Stepankova|first8=Katerina|last9=Nadel|first9=Lynn|access-date=2021-04-05|archive-date=2019-03-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190330035708/https://www.frontiersin.org/articles/10.3389/fnhum.2015.00431/full|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 结构 ==
海马旁回分为前部和后部：前部包含[[钩回|钩回]]，与[[鼻周皮层|鼻周皮层]]（有包含关系）、[[内嗅皮层|内嗅皮层]]、[[后鼻皮层|后鼻皮层]]联系紧密；后部[[舌回|舌回]]相连<ref name=":0" /><ref>{{Cite web|title=Entorhinal cortex|url=https://radiopaedia.org/articles/entorhinal-cortex?lang=us|accessdate=2021-04-05|last=Gaillard|first=Frank|work=Radiopaedia|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-04-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210420004436/https://radiopaedia.org/articles/entorhinal-cortex?lang=us|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

海马旁回是枕颞内侧回（medial occipitotemporal gyrus）的一部分、另一部分为[[舌回|舌回]]，与下方的[[梭状回|梭状回]]（枕颞外侧回）相对应<ref name=":22">{{Cite web|title=Medial occipitotemporal gyrus|url=https://radiopaedia.org/articles/medial-occipitotemporal-gyrus?lang=us|access-date=2021-05-31|last=Gaillard|first=Frank|work=Radiopaedia|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-11-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211105043548/https://radiopaedia.org/articles/medial-occipitotemporal-gyrus?lang=us|dead-url=no}}</ref>。海马旁回与梭状回之间有[[侧副裂|侧副裂]]隔开<ref name=":22" />。

== 功能 ==
海马旁回位置区域（parahippocampal place area）在认知和存储环境场景的过程中扮演重要角色<ref name=":1">{{Cite journal|title=Seeing Scenes: Topographic Visual Hallucinations Evoked by Direct Electrical Stimulation of the Parahippocampal Place Area|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC6608225/|last=Mégevand|first=Pierre|last2=Groppe|first2=David M.|date=2014-04-16|journal=The Journal of Neuroscience|issue=16|doi=10.1523/JNEUROSCI.5202-13.2014|volume=34|pages=5399–5405|issn=0270-6474|pmc=6608225|pmid=24741031|last3=Goldfinger|first3=Matthew S.|last4=Hwang|first4=Sean T.|last5=Kingsley|first5=Peter B.|last6=Davidesco|first6=Ido|last7=Mehta|first7=Ashesh D.}}</ref><ref name=":2">{{Cite journal|title=A cortical representation of the local visual environment|url=http://adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/1998Natur.392..598E|last=Epstein|first=Russell|last2=Kanwisher|first2=Nancy|date=1998-04-01|journal=Nature|doi=10.1038/33402|volume=392|pages=598–601|issn=0028-0836|access-date=2021-04-05|archive-date=2018-11-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181106232314/http://adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/1998Natur.392..598E|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[功能性磁共振成像|功能性磁共振成像]]研究发现，该区域在测试者观察地形场景过程中高度活跃，包括风景、城市景观以及房间等<ref name=":1" /><ref name=":2" />。该区域损伤的患者，能够认知场景中的具体事物（如人、家具等），但无法认知场景<ref>{{Cite journal|title=The Parahippocampus Subserves Topographical Learning in Man|url=https://doi.org/10.1093/cercor/6.6.823|last=Aguirre|first=Geoffrey K.|last2=Detre|first2=John A.|date=1996-11-01|journal=Cerebral Cortex|issue=6|doi=10.1093/cercor/6.6.823|volume=6|pages=823–829|issn=1047-3211|last3=Alsop|first3=David C.|last4=D'Esposito|first4=Mark}}</ref>。

== 临床 ==
海马旁回与部分{{le|海马硬化|Hippocampal sclerosis}}的病例有关<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Analysis of parahippocampal gyrus in 115 patients with hippocampal sclerosis|url=http://www.scielo.br/scielo.php?script=sci_abstract&pid=S0004-282X2003000500001&lng=en&nrm=iso&tlng=en|last=Ferreira|first=Nelson Fortes|last2=Oliveira|first2=Vanessa de|date=2003-09|journal=Arquivos de Neuro-Psiquiatria|issue=3B|doi=10.1590/S0004-282X2003000500001|volume=61|pages=707–711|language=en|issn=0004-282X|last3=Amaral|first3=Lázaro|last4=Mendonça|first4=Renato|last5=Lima|first5=Sérgio Santos}}</ref>。在一些[[精神分裂|精神分裂]]的患者中，海马旁回出现不对称<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Anomalous Asymmetry of Fusiform and Parahippocampal Gyrus Gray Matter in Schizophrenia: A Postmortem Study|url=https://ajp.psychiatryonline.org/doi/full/10.1176/ajp.157.1.40|last=McDonald|first=Brendan|last2=Highley|first2=J. Robin|date=2000-01-01|journal=American Journal of Psychiatry|issue=1|doi=10.1176/ajp.157.1.40|volume=157|pages=40–47|issn=0002-953X|last3=Walker|first3=Mary A.|last4=Herron|first4=Brian M.|last5=Cooper|first5=Stephen J.|last6=Esiri|first6=Margaret M.|last7=Crow|first7=Timothy J.|access-date=2021-04-05|archive-date=2019-07-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190719105211/https://ajp.psychiatryonline.org/doi/full/10.1176/ajp.157.1.40|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

